  "excerpt": "<p>If you had coverage through Medicare, Medicaid, the Children\u2019s Health Insurance Program (CHIP), or another source, depending on the coverage you had, you may get Form 1095-B, Health Coverage, to help you complete your taxes.</p>",
  "content": "<p>If you had coverage through <a href=\"/node/40166\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8650aac3-9ebb-4527-bd29-8639439d82ba\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40166\" data-entity-bundle=\"brief\" title=\"Medicare (term tolltip)\">Medicare</a>, <a href=\"/glossary/medicaid\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"13c0081d-9e96-420a-a724-6e81e89d20c1\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"35311\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" title=\"Medicaid\">Medicaid</a>, the <a href=\"/glossary/childrens-health-insurance-program-chip\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"87f4b3ac-b0c4-45b7-a691-d5b2cc35aac3\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"35631\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" title=\"Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP)\">Children\u2019s Health Insurance Program (CHIP)</a>, or another source, depending on the coverage you had, you may get Form 1095-B, Health Coverage, to help you complete your taxes.</p><h2>1. If you get Form 1095-B</h2><ul><li>You should have it by mid-March.</li><li>Read Parts III and IV to find information about:<ul><li>Your 2025 health coverage</li><li>Covered individuals and the months they had coverage</li></ul></li></ul><h2>2. Complete your tax return</h2><p>Don't include Form 1095-B with your federal tax return. Keep it with your other tax documents.</p><h3>Tax forms and instructions:</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/f1040.pdf\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"6e53decb-cbd9-410d-b50d-c544e43f62aa\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40496\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"IRS Form 1040 - 2025\">Form 1040, U.S. Individual Income Tax Return</a> (PDF, 215 KB) and <a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/i1040gi.pdf\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"bb01966e-6b89-4a2e-82f7-176af7927fad\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40501\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"IRS Form 1040 Instructions - 2025\">Form 1040 instructions</a> (PDF, 4.2 MB)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/Affordable-Care-Act/Questions-and-Answers-about-Health-Care-Information-Forms-for-Individuals\">Questions and answers about Forms 1095-B or 1095-C from the IRS</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/filing/individuals/how-to-file\">Find help preparing and filing your taxes.</a></li><li><a href=\"/how-can-i-protect-myself-from-tax-scams\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"90d7219e-fa4d-49d8-9a65-3adb840014ba\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36086\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Protect yourself from tax scams\">Protect yourself from tax scams.</a></li></ul><h2>More than one type of coverage?</h2><p>If you had other coverage for only part of 2025, or other household members had different coverage, select the other coverage:</p><ul><li><a href=\"/taxes/marketplace-plan-with-savings\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"9a183698-0dcb-4817-9e65-9f7fccf6bbb6\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36171\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had a Marketplace plan with the premium tax credit\">Marketplace plan with the premium tax credit</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes/marketplace-plan-without-savings\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"a0921806-0c09-4403-a273-eecd83603d95\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36176\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had a Marketplace plan without the premium tax credit\">Marketplace plan without the premium tax credit</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes/job-based-insurance\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"f00713df-ce1f-4edd-8afb-94ab4c8e54a5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36166\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had job-based health coverage\">Job-based health coverage</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes/no-health-coverage\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"93040ce0-073c-4f7f-98ba-ad888b9375fc\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36181\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had no health coverage\">No health coverage</a></li></ul><div data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"21885ea5-8cc5-4b26-ab46-691347e9bcf3\" data-embed-button=\"brief\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:node.inline\" data-langcode=\"en\" data-entity-embed-display-settings=\"[]\" class=\"embedded-entity\">\n<article class=\"node node--type-brief node--view-mode-inline\">\n\n  \n    \n\n  \n  <div class=\"node__content\">\n    \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-content-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item\"><h2>Other tax years</h2><ul><li><a href=\"/taxes-2024/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"b33efc77-6f55-4e10-b324-31969274517a\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40431\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2024 federal income tax return\">2024 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2023/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"4a81c2e1-4c04-48f1-a6e7-e3297ce41cec\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40261\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2023 federal income tax return\">2023 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2022/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8d6d56f2-e511-49bd-9b10-d2418687d6f5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39826\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2022 federal income tax return\">2022 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2021/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"0f722923-3f01-4ee5-a880-903622d6d43b\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"38236\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2021 federal income tax return\">2021 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2020/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"1c1ea020-180c-4959-9f3c-4fb1a8fa7d51\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36766\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2020 federal income tax return\">2020 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2019/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8d9b1ebd-930d-4552-a3b6-482a707d9894\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36736\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2019 federal income tax return\">2019 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2018/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8b6e5121-9911-4ee8-8bb3-a6a5705475a5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36706\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2018 federal income tax return\">2018 taxes</a></li></ul></div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n",
